Package votebox.middle

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBallotVars
    An object that implements IGlobalVars knows all the necessary path and filename information for a single ballot.
    IVoteboxConstants
    These are configurable constants that votebox uses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Event
    Because this code was originally designed for C#, there are a few places that use the C# event primitive.
    Properties
    The properties class is used to store, in the state of any ballot or layout object, properties that are declared in the corresponding XML file.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IncorrectTypeException
    This exception is thrown when an assumption is made about a type that is false.
    UnknownFormatException
    This exception is thrown by Properties if the format given for a certain type cannot be decoded to mean anything reasonable.
    UnknownTypeException
    This method is thrown by Properties when it encounters a type it doesn't know about.
